H0.text: In the Star Wars series of films what is the name of the slug-like alien who had a bounty on Han Solo, who owed him money for dumping an illegal cargo. Jabba the Hutt

H1.text: In the Star Wars series of films what is the name of the slug-like alien who had a bounty on Han Solo, who owed him money for dumping an illegal cargo. Watto

H2.text: In the Star Wars series of films what is the name of the slug-like alien who had a bounty on Han Solo, who owed him money for dumping an illegal cargo. Greedo

H3.text: In the Star Wars series of films what is the name of the slug-like alien who had a bounty on Han Solo, who owed him money for dumping an illegal cargo. Ghoel

A4.text: Watto is a Toydarian, a slug-like alien species.

A5.text: Watto is a mean-tempered, greedy Toydarian who owns a second-hand goods store in Mos Espa on Tatooine.
